<div class="row">
	<header class="col-12">
		<h1>A Simple and Basic Responsive Grid Based on Creatix CSS</h1>
		<ul>
		 <li>All columns widths are specified as percentages</li>
		 <li>Multi-column layout automatically change to a single column for small viewport devices and resized broswers on desktops</li>
		 <li>Stylesheet is coded in <a href="http://sass-lang.com/" target="_blank">Sass</a> with gutter margin defined as a single variable and is therefore adjustable to suit page/site requirements</li>
		 <li>Images wider than the columns they're contained in resize automatically to fit column width</li>
		</ul>
		<p>This header is inside a flexbox grid 12 columns wide</p>
	</header>
</div>

